  "summary": {
    "en": [
      "<p>This miniature on the silicate mineral mica was made by an unknown Indian artist. Likely sold as part of a souvenir set, miniatures like these depicted occupational types of Indian subjects to feed into European exoticizing sensibilities.</p>"
    ]
  },
